# Source artwork / local scratch — the served canvases now live in
# public/canvas/ (.pdf files). The repo-root Canvas/ folder holds
# 44 MB of source working copies and shouldn't ship. Anchor with a
# leading "/" so the rule does NOT also match public/canvas/ on
# case-insensitive filesystems (macOS / Windows default).
/Canvas/
